<% provide(:title, "About") %>
<div class="large-8 small-centered columns">
  <% if flash[:notice].present? %>
    <div data-alert class="alert-box">
      <%= flash[:notice] %>
      <a href="#" class="close">&times;</a>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <h1>
    About Me
  </h1>
  <p>
    Hey guys! I'm Danny.<br />
    I'm currently a Senior at Binghamton University, majoring in Computer Science.
  </p>
  <p>
    Creating web apps enables me to tune into my creative side, as well as make use of my problem solving skills. I find it addictively fun. <br />
    As a result, you can find me tinkering with <i class="fi-laptop"></i> Ruby/Rails, <i class="fi-music"></i> playing guitar/singing, or <i class="fi-torsos"></i> running in my spare time.
  </p>
  <p>
    Currently looking for an entry-level Ruby on Rails developer position or internship!
  </p>

  <div class="txt-msg-section">
  <h4>
    Want to shoot me a text?
  </h4>
  <%= form_tag about_path, :method => :get do %>
    <%= text_field_tag :name, nil, placeholder: "Name" %>
    <%= text_area_tag :message, nil, placeholder: "Hi Danny! You can reach me back at me@example.com." %>
    <%= submit_tag "Send Text", class: "button tiny radius" %>
  <% end %>
</div>
</div>